value.0: This beautiful Moon Elf stands with a relaxed composure as you approach her. From her hands, the element of water appears to flow from her body and promptly dampening the floor. Her tone is stress-free and slow, her eyes gaze over you as she speaks.
This massive Frog linger intimidatingly at you. With strange spikes along its back, you can tell it's a Dire Toad.
Soft and silky cushions feel terrific on your battle weary buttocks...
